On the evolution of neural decisions from uncertain visual input to uncertain actions

Alessandro Tomassini1*, Darren Price1, Jiaxiang Zhang2, James B Rowe1, 3

1. Medical Research Council Cognition and Brain Sciences Unit, University of Cambridge, CB27EF, UK
2. Cardiff University Brain Research Imaging Centre, School of Psychology, University of Cardiff, CF2 2AT, UK
3. Department of Clinical Neurosciences, University of Cambridge, CB2 0SZ, UK

